      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<li>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.1",
      "en": "Manage VMs across AWS, Azure, Google Cloud, and on-premise infrastructure from one interface",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.10",
      "en": "We used to juggle a dozen consoles. With Electros , it feels like one window onto millions of machines worldwide—whether we need a beefy CPU host , a GPU-heavy stack for AI, or something in between.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.11",
      "en": "When we need something more exotic on-prem , we still reach for the same interface . That consistency is what sold us.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.12",
      "en": "Powerful capabilities for managing hybrid and multicloud environments",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.13",
      "en": "Deploy VMs across public clouds and private nodes seamlessly, balancing cost, performance, and compliance.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.14",
      "en": "Connect via SSH, VNC, or RDP with a single click from the desktop app.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.15",
      "en": "Automate infrastructure-as-code. Electros CLI powers scripting, CI/CD, and cloud pipeline workflows.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.16",
      "en": "Experience the unified interface for managing your cloud infrastructure",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.17",
      "en": "Embed a screenshot or carousel of the app UI showing VM list and remote session capabilities.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.18",
      "en": "[Demo image placeholder - Electros App desktop interface showing VM list and remote session]",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.19",
      "en": "Seamless connectivity across all your virtual machines with intelligent protocol selection",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.2",
      "en": "Auto-select SSH, RDP, or VNC protocols based on your VM's operating system",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.20",
      "en": "Electros provides intelligent remote access that automatically selects the optimal protocol based on your VM's operating system and configuration. Whether you're connecting to Linux servers, Windows workstations, or specialized appliances, Electros ensures you get the best possible remote experience.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.21",
      "en": "Secure shell access for Linux, BSD, and Unix systems",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.22",
      "en": "Remote Desktop Protocol for Windows and Linux GUI sessions",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.23",
      "en": "Virtual Network Computing for cross-platform graphical access",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.24",
      "en": "Intelligent protocol detection based on guest OS",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.25",
      "en": "Coming soon: 4K at 60fps remote streaming",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.26",
      "en": "Get started with the Electros orchestration dashboard",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.27",
      "en": "Native applications for your operating system with full GUI capabilities.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.28",
      "en": "How Electros works behind the scenes",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.29",
      "en": "Electros combines a desktop app with elemento-cli, backed by core services for hybrid and multicloud work. It automatically selects the appropriate protocol based on the guest OS—SSH for Linux, RDP/VNC for Windows—and keeps operations coherent across environments.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.3",
      "en": "Use elemento-cli for scripting and pipelines alongside the desktop app",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.30",
      "en": "Desktop and CLI build on the same foundations for VMs, storage, and networking. Today some flows are richer in one surface than the other; alignment improves with each release.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.31",
      "en": "Comprehensive support across operating systems and access protocols",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.32",
      "en": "Common questions about Electros functionality",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.33",
      "en": "Yes, basic inventory and local VM management work without network, syncing when online.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.34",
      "en": "Yes. Both use the same core services, but coverage differs—some tasks are desktop-first or CLI-first today. Check release notes for what each surface supports.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.35",
      "en": "SSH (Linux/BSD), RDP/VNC (Windows/Linux GUI). 4K streaming is coming soon.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.36",
      "en": "Yes, Electros is free with your Elemento account. No additional licensing fees required.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.37",
      "en": "Experience the power of Electros for unified multicloud management",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.4",
      "en": "Electros is Elemento Cloud's orchestration dashboard—available as a native desktop app (Linux, macOS, Windows) and CLI. It provides cohesive visibility, provisioning, and remote access for workloads across any integrated infrastructure.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.5",
      "en": "Whether you're managing VMs on AWS , Azure , Google Cloud , or your own on-premise infrastructure , Electros gives you a unified interface for complete control.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.6",
      "en": "Surfaces to run Linux, macOS, Windows apps, plus elemento-cli",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.7",
      "en": "Cloud & hybrid targets AWS, Azure, Google Cloud, and on-prem infrastructure",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.8",
      "en": "Stack integrations AtomOS and Atomosphere for provisioning and control",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.electros.p.9",
      "en": "Ship-ready builds AppImage, DMG, EXE, and DEB—x64 and ARM64 where supported",
      "it": "",
      "source": "electros.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
